{"id":1404,"date":"2015-05-21T20:17:35","date_gmt":"2015-05-22T03:17:35","slug":"pro-bono-promo-helas-sporting-club","title":"PRO BONO PROMO: Helas Sporting Club","content":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/krak/id916474561?mt=8\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-1405\" src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_300/mag/uploads/Helas-Polo-Club-Lucas-Puig-1.png\" alt=\"Helas Polo Club Lucas Puig 1\" width=\"300\" height=\"169\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_300/mag/uploads/Helas-Polo-Club-Lucas-Puig-1.png 300w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_1024/mag/uploads/Helas-Polo-Club-Lucas-Puig-1.png 1024w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_1080/mag/uploads/Helas-Polo-Club-Lucas-Puig-1.png 1080w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/mag/uploads/Helas-Polo-Club-Lucas-Puig-1.png 1090w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a><a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/krak/id916474561?mt=8\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-1407\" src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_300/mag/uploads/Helas-Polo-Club-Lucas-Puig.png\" alt=\"Helas Polo Club Lucas Puig\" width=\"300\" height=\"169\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_300/mag/uploads/Helas-Polo-Club-Lucas-Puig.png 300w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_1024/mag/uploads/Helas-Polo-Club-Lucas-Puig.png 1024w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_1080/mag/uploads/Helas-Polo-Club-Lucas-Puig.png 1080w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/mag/uploads/Helas-Polo-Club-Lucas-Puig.png 1091w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Unless you&#8217;ve been living under a rock for the last couple of years, you&#8217;ve probably heard of Lucas Puig&#8217;s <a href=\"http://helascaps.com\" target=\"_blank\">Helas Caps</a> brand. Aside from bringing a totally new aesthetic to the skate hat game (with a clever play on the Polo aesthetic), Helas has been nothing short of an endless fountain of <del>cream soda</del> amazing skate edits. Whether it&#8217;s an edit of iPhone clips or VX throwaways, you can bet that every one of their shorts are top notch. The latest Helas Sporting Club edit is again no different, bringing the heat with four and a half minutes of goodness and is filmed primarily around Barcy with a couple of clips from Shanghai. Featuring Lucas Puig, Luypa Sin, Jesus Fernandez, Javier Sarmiento, Thierry Gormit, Marek Zaprazny, Roman Lisivka, Pedro Attenborough, Jose Vivero Diaz, JB Gillet, Max Geronzi, Charles Collet, Stephen Khou, Alex Maison, Kristian Krasimirov, JP Villa and Karl Salah.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Luy Pa Sin with a backtail shove out at MACBA.</em></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/krak/id916474561?mt=8\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\" size-medium wp-image-1408 aligncenter\" src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_300/mag/uploads/Helas-Polo-Club-Luy-Pa-Sin.png\" alt=\"Helas Polo Club Luy Pa Sin\" width=\"300\" height=\"169\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_300/mag/uploads/Helas-Polo-Club-Luy-Pa-Sin.png 300w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_1024/mag/uploads/Helas-Polo-Club-Luy-Pa-Sin.png 1024w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_1080/mag/uploads/Helas-Polo-Club-Luy-Pa-Sin.png 1080w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/mag/uploads/Helas-Polo-Club-Luy-Pa-Sin.png 1091w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a>Definitely super psyched to see footage of Luy Pa Sin ripping, and his pop shove front crook at Plaza Universitat is worth a watch alone. Jesus Fernandez really lights up Sants with a fakie flip crooks, fakie pop shove switch 5-0 180 out followed up with a back 3 down the curb. Now say that again really quick. And if you blink you might miss Javier Sarmiento&#8217;s cameo at Sants as well!</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Jesus Fernandez mid-line with a fakie flip crooks at Sants.</em></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/krak/id916474561?mt=8\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\" size-medium wp-image-1410 aligncenter\" src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_300/mag/uploads/Helas-Polo-Club-Jesus-Fernandez.png\" alt=\"Helas Polo Club Jesus Fernandez\" width=\"300\" height=\"169\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_300/mag/uploads/Helas-Polo-Club-Jesus-Fernandez.png 300w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_1024/mag/uploads/Helas-Polo-Club-Jesus-Fernandez.png 1024w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_1080/mag/uploads/Helas-Polo-Club-Jesus-Fernandez.png 1080w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/mag/uploads/Helas-Polo-Club-Jesus-Fernandez.png 1092w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a></p>\n<p>We all know that Marek Zaprazny is a beast on the board, and his kickflip over a Jersey barrier off flat followed by a high speed back tail is more than enough of a reminder of that fact.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Marek Zaprazny with a kickflip over a Jersey barrier off flat.</em></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/krak/id916474561?mt=8\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-1409\" src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_300/mag/uploads/Helas-Polo-Club-Marek-Zaprazny.png\" alt=\"Helas Polo Club Marek Zaprazny\" width=\"300\" height=\"169\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_300/mag/uploads/Helas-Polo-Club-Marek-Zaprazny.png 300w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_1024/mag/uploads/Helas-Polo-Club-Marek-Zaprazny.png 1024w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_1080/mag/uploads/Helas-Polo-Club-Marek-Zaprazny.png 1080w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/mag/uploads/Helas-Polo-Club-Marek-Zaprazny.png 1090w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a></p>\n<p>This whole edit is chock full of amazing skating and definitely proof that in this age of over saturated skateboard media content, sometimes less is more. And of course Lucas closes the video out with a banger! Peep the edit and get hyped already! &#8211; HK</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Lucas Puig with a noseslide nollie backside heel out.</em></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/krak/id916474561?mt=8\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-1406\" src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_300/mag/uploads/Helas-Polo-Club-Lucas-Puig-2.png\" alt=\"Helas Polo Club Lucas Puig 2\" width=\"300\" height=\"168\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_300/mag/uploads/Helas-Polo-Club-Lucas-Puig-2.png 300w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_1024/mag/uploads/Helas-Polo-Club-Lucas-Puig-2.png 1024w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_1080/mag/uploads/Helas-Polo-Club-Lucas-Puig-2.png 1080w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/mag/uploads/Helas-Polo-Club-Lucas-Puig-2.png 1090w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a></p>\n<p><iframe src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/128003439\" width=\"640\" height=\"480\" frameborder=\"0\" title=\"H&eacute;las Sporting Club\" webkitallowfullscreen mozallowfullscreen allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n","author":"kev","categories":["reviews"],"tags":["alex-maison","barcelona","charles-collet","helas-caps","javier-sarmiento","jb-gillet","jesus-fernandez","jose-vivero-diaz","jp-villa","karl-salah"],"featuredImages":[{"file":"Helas-Polo-Club-Lucas-Puig.png","width":1091,"height":613,"mime_type":"image/png","source_url":"https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/mag/uploads/Helas-Polo-Club-Lucas-Puig.png"}],"video":""}